snippet.title: Amber Laura Heard Transformation *then and now* (1992-2021) part 1 #shorts
snippet.description:
Amber Laura Heard (born April 22, 1986 in Austin, Texas, USA) is an American actress. He made his acting debut in 2004 in Billy Bob Thornton's Friday Night Lights, a sports drama starring in North Country and Alpha Dogta in small-scale roles. His first role was as Mandy Lane in All The Boys Love Mandy (2006). played and then The CW's Hidden Palms in 2007.
